====================================
Documentation 

Getting Started (Free Edition):    http://docs.datomic.com/getting-started.html
Setting Up Storage (Pro Edition):  http://docs.datomic.com/storage.html 
All docs:                          http://datomic.com

====================================
Install in your local maven repos:

Replace DATOMIC_VERSION in the snippet below with the contents of the 
VERSION file at the root of this distribution.

mvn install:install-file -DgroupId=com.datomic -DartifactId=datomic-free -Dfile=datomic-free-${DATOMIC-VERSION}.jar -DpomFile=pom.xml

====================================
Using from maven:

Replace DATOMIC_VERSION in the snippet below with the contents of the 
VERSION file at the root of this distribution. Then add the snippet to the 
dependencies section of your pom.xml:

    <dependency>
      <groupId>com.datomic</groupId>
      <artifactId>datomic-free</artifactId>
      <version>${DATOMIC_VERSION}</version>
    </dependency>

====================================
Using from leiningen:

Replace DATOMIC_VERSION in the snippet below with the contents of the 
VERSION file at the root of this distribution. Then add the snippet to the 
dependencies section of your project.clj:

   [com.datomic/datomic-free "${DATOMIC_VERSION}"]




